ass you or your children as you walk to/from this motel. The single phone in the room was across the room from the bed. If someone in your family is sick and needs a prescription, there is no need to locate a pharmacy. Any drug is available on a multitude of street corners easily within walking distance of this motel. Bon Voyage!	
